Text: RE HelloPST Chris Friday is cool with me My appointment is on the north end and will end around pm If we say pm that will give me some grace and also time to travel Let me know where and what time works for you Talk with you soon Trace Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday January AM To Traci McBride Subject RE Hello Traci I am really looking forward to my cooking class My first one is this Saturday morning Im a little scared I am going to be the class screw up Oh well I wont know untill I try I think I am going to Yoga on Wednesday but dinner on Friday would be great Give me a shout or drop me an email and let me know what time you want to eat and Ill make some reservations Talk to you soon Chris Original Message From Traci McBride ENRON Sent Tuesday January AM To Dorland Chris Subject Hello Good Morning I am having a crazy week At least it is keeping me out of trouble I really enjoyed seeing you again as well It is good to see that you are doing so well I have two appointments this week in Calgary Wednesday I have two and Friday afternoon another If you want to get together either Wednesday for Coffee after sometime or Friday for a later dinner after sometime let me know Good luck with your cooking classes Hopefully all appendages remain attached Talk with you soon Traci Original Message From Dorland Chris mailtoChris NRONcom Sent Tuesday January AM To Traci McBride Subject hope your week is going well Traci Great seeing you again and catching up Be sure to give me a shout if you are coming to Calgary Dont work too hard Chris a St SW Calgary Alberta RE Good MorningPST Hello Sorry I didnt get back to you yesterday I have been extremely busy I am around on that weekend I am supposed to be at a conference that weekend However if the teachers are still on strike the conference will be cancelled Heres hoping It will be good to see you guys that weekend When you know give me a shout and let me know what your schedule is like We can tee something up around the conference even if it is a go I dont know about you but I am really getting sick of this weather I want to get out to BanffLouise and get some skiingboarding in Remind me when you are down and I will give you that cleansing info Looks like I am going to start me cleanse on Friday I am loading up on all the beef sugar and wheat I can Its hell but those are the foods I really miss while cleansing Better run Have clients coming in shortly Have a good one Trace Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday January AM To Traci McBride Subject RE Good Morning Hi Traci I had a very relaxing weekend Slept hours both nights Worked out and chilled Very good weekend except for the weather No worries about Friday The highways were ridiculous My brother is coming to town on Thursday for a week It will be good to see him I am planning on being in Red Deer on the weekend of the th Maybe we can get together then Let me know if you are freeHave a great week and I will speak to you soon Chris Original Message From Traci McBride ENRON Sent Tuesday January AM To Dorland Chris Subject Good Morning Hello Chris All appendages still attached Hope you enjoyed your cooking class and had an enjoyable weekend Sorry I had to cancel on Friday weather here is still awful Have a good week Traci Traci McBride Investment Advisor Raymond James Ltd Ph email This email and any files transmitted
